{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reverse the decision to weaken planned oil sanctions on Russia",
        "additional_details": "We further believe this is a decision that will cost Ukrainian lives, civilian and military, as well as our moral leadership over this war: it must be reversed, now.",
        "background": "On 20 May 2026 the Government announced its decision to reduce its planned sanctions on Russian oil. In so doing we believe it is helping directly fund Russia's war machine against Ukraine.",
